text: Stella Tennant (17 December 1970 âˆ’ 22 December 2020) was a British model and fashion designer. She posed for a number of magazines, including the French, British and Italian versions of Vogue. Tennant was born in London. In June 2012, Tennant was honored as Model of the Year in the Scottish Fashion Awards Hall of Fame at its annual awards. Tennant died suddenly on 22 December 2020 in Duns, Scottish Borders at the age of 50. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Models from London
